{"tid":411441,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"文科嚟講樹仁大學係唔係屌打八大？","createTime":"2017-09-23T18:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T19:01:09.000Z","uid":81572,"like":60,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9efb8a229402094de32a2653f4735d1763696cb0","tid":411441,"uid":81572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日我搭車個陣聽到車前邊有兩個人喺度傾計<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> A:你讀完asso升樹仁會唔會好唔甘心？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> B:唔會吔，我其實有教大offer，不過我覺得樹仁讀中文會專業好多，依家香港來講文科最好一定係樹&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> A: 唔會啩，其他先唔講中大、港大點可能輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> B：樹仁係全港最專業的，乜你冇聽過 站在樹仁的肩上，可以看得更遠咩，喺度讀我好開心囉<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜依家樹仁咁勁吤咩，asso仔有ugc都唔讀要揀樹大"},{"pid":"16577e0f4f6a39f57f9fd00176b5addc948e4d9b","tid":411441,"uid":145588,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"讀文科都係乞食架姐 不用分得那麼細"},{"pid":"a11f4d8c87aac967668d33b5e53532f4a578bc54","tid":411441,"uid":81625,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:10:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦樹仁，浸教嶺是但一間都屌打佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6c201d4e67be719410827cdc503c297fe16ef1","tid":411441,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:40:35.000Z","msg":"樹仁中文係唔差 但係會唔會勁過中大中文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5070781aa654523c60924e890830b3c2598ed614","tid":411441,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樹仁中