 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪有樹仁仔得罪左樓主"},{"pid":"da02be993abc86098ab2fb01c41747d7189962d2","tid":411441,"uid":81572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樹仁仔真係特別on9</blockquote><br />\n樓主唔講出黎鬼有人理佢咩<br />\n由佢地自成一國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係唔明樹仁有咁好咩？個asso仔有八大都唔讀揀樹仁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我懷疑個asso仔其實好廢，純吹水打丁，真實咩offer都無嘅可憐蟲"},{"pid":"7bd2c7eb28bdd70f60212e4fa0adcfd2ea4c2f8a","tid":411441,"uid":142212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樹仁是一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216a1f8c11de96aa8b64da8e46f492f6eb063cba","tid":411441,"uid":148994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"中文系嚟講算係有把炮過，但真係唔係依家，亦係因為教授勁，佢地知識先有得扎實嘅機會。近幾年帶老頂出席講座，都仲見到有唔錯嘅師資，可惜佢濫收埋啲又冇品又冇知識嘅學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地固步自封就一定，好少但又唔係冇地，難見到有創新思維嘅學生。講咁多做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之佢地想做中學生，唔好要求咁多，反正第日都係想做教畜，都唔係為貢獻社會同文明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n（利申：依家做緊嘅職位，會做吓論文審批嘅工作）"},{"pid":"8d51e2998ab86d93b65872e724f78770b731c933","tid":411441,"uid":144549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"樹仁新傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自覺唔差..."},{"pid":"c5c303d0da8f1265c7902aad68606d4e5bd2eae7","tid":411441,"uid":149634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"i大仲勁啦屌你"},{"pid":"85d604591227575886e4d40e5b39d99c6abc53a7","tid":411441,"uid":12415,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2